{"word":"G4834 - συμπαθέω - sympathéō - soom-path-eh'-o - Have compassion","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμπαθέω</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">sympathéō</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-path-eh'-o</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Have compassion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Verb / வினைச்சொல்</span>"},{"paragraph":"வினைச்சொல் - பரிதபி"},{"paragraph":"1. to be affected with the same feeling as another, to sympathize with"},{"paragraph":"2. in reference to the wretched, to feel for, have compassion on"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G4835 - συμπαθής - sympathḗs - soom-path-ace'/4835\">G4835</a>; to <i>feel</i> &ldquo;sympathy&rdquo; with, that is, (by implication) to <i>commiserate:</i> - have compassion, be touched with a feeling of.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G2552/2552\">G2552</a>, <a href=\"#/G2553/2553\">G2553</a>, <a href=\"#/G3356/3356\">G3356</a>, <a href=\"#/G3663/3663\">G3663</a>, <a href=\"#/G3804/3804\">G3804</a>, <a href=\"#/G3805/3805\">G3805</a>, <a href=\"#/G3806/3806\">G3806</a>, <a href=\"#/G3958/3958\">G3958</a>, <a href=\"#/G4236/4236\">G4236</a>, <a href=\"#/G4310/4310\">G4310</a>, <a href=\"#/G4777/4777\">G4777</a>, <a href=\"#/G4834/4834\">G4834</a>, <a href=\"#/G4835/4835\">G4835</a>, <a href=\"#/G4841/4841\">G4841</a>"}]}